milestones.description: Mohammad Rafique has become the top wicket-taker for BAN in ODIs with 66 wickets, going past Khaled Mahmud's 65
Mohammad Rafique and Aftab Ahmed's 150-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 89 between Rajin Saleh and Aftab Ahmed
Mohammad Rafique has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (52) in an innings in ODIs for BAN, going past Mohammad Rafique's 50
Mohammad Rafique has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for BAN, going past Habibul Bashar's 3
